reviewText: If you want to learn about what it takes to give a massage then this DVD is for you. No I don't plan on giving massages I just wanted to see what it takes. Informative but NOT sexy.
great....so precise and easy to understand...would advise buying this...every body area covered... didn't take long to get in the mail

I bought this DVD to learn on how to give a good massage to my wife. The instructor is easy to understand and is very clear to the point. The set up is good and the clarity of the DVD is very nice. I have learned a lot from this DVD and I look forward to apply what I have learned. I would recommend this one to any one who would like to learn how to give good massage.
